Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "State Trooper Clark C. Lewis Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system in the town of East Hampton, county of Suffolk, as the "State Trooper Clark C. Lewis Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "State Trooper Clark C. Lewis Memorial Highway"
